code: @Bean @ConditionalOnMissingBean public WebServiceTemplateBuilder webServiceTemplateBuilder(ObjectProvider<WebServiceTemplateCustomizer> webServiceTemplateCustomizers) {     WebServiceTemplateBuilder builder = new WebServiceTemplateBuilder().     List<WebServiceTemplateCustomizer> customizers = webServiceTemplateCustomizers.orderedStream().collect(Collectors.toList()).     if (!customizers.isEmpty()) {         builder = builder.customizers(customizers).     }     return builder. }
